The paper presents an information theoretic analysis of the impact of insertion-deletion errors in nanopore sequencers, which involves the study of fundamental bounds and approaches to sequence reconstruction. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Computational Complexity (cs.CC) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
